{"tid":1141354,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 張鎬濂撐阿媽洪欣 刪微博張丹峰合照","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T12:27:06.000Z","uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1cab85163405737e0b38faedb0744a2dd0ca7fba","tid":1141354,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:13:29.000Z","msg":"張丹峰疑偷食經理人畢瀅事件曝光後，洪欣已即時怒刪網上與張丹峰的合照，兼一直都未有為張丹峰發聲，二人關係跌至新低點。雖然早前張丹峰發出聲明，表示一切屬造假，但未能令洪欣投下信任票，二人關係未見改善。<br />\n<br />\n日前，洪欣兒子張鎬濂亦被發現刪除微博上與張丹峰的合照，只剩下一張祝張丹峰生日快樂的相片，張鎬濂此舉，被視為是表態撐阿媽洪欣，看來多年父子情，隨時凍過水。"},{"pid":"dd784d72b0346b4ceb716506eb35f892a0e57d98","tid":1141354,"uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QEUfZFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQEUfZFS.png&h=f62b5ddb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff49ec964d037e69c4b3a775528874146fe29e42","tid":1141354,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8w2Yc5k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8w2Yc5k.png&h=5f3d51a1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}